{{short description|Swiss index of degree of globalisation by country}}
The '''KOF Index of Globalisation''' is an [[List of globalization-related indices|index]] of the degree of [[globalisation]] of 122 countries.{{r|axel|page=29}} It was conceived by [[Axel Dreher]] at the Konjunkturforschungsstelle of [[ETH Zurich]], in Switzerland. It was first published in 2002, and covered the period from 1970 until that year.{{r|marco|page=46}} A new version of it was published in 2017.{{r|axel|page=29}}

The index is based on three principal criteria: economic, political and social.{{r|marco|page=46}} Unlike the [[Maastricht Globalisation Index]], it does not take into account [[Environmental quality|environmental]] factors.{{r|axel|page=29}}

